LABEL arch
TEXT HELP
Boot the Arch Modern install medium on BIOS.
It allows you to install Arch Modern or perform system maintenance.
ENDTEXT
MENU LABEL Arch Modern install medium (@@ARCH@@, BIOS)
LINUX /@@INSTALL_DIR@@/boot/@@ARCH@@/@@KERNEL_FILE@@
INITRD /@@INSTALL_DIR@@/boot/@@ARCH@@/@@INITRAMFS_FILE@@
APPEND archisobasedir=@@INSTALL_DIR@@ archisolabel=@@ISO_LABEL@@ @@BOOT_CMDLINE@@

LABEL archrescue
TEXT HELP
Boot in rescue/maintenance mode (nomodeset).
ENDTEXT
MENU LABEL Arch Modern Rescue Mode (nomodeset)
LINUX /@@INSTALL_DIR@@/boot/@@ARCH@@/@@KERNEL_FILE@@
INITRD /@@INSTALL_DIR@@/boot/@@ARCH@@/@@INITRAMFS_FILE@@
APPEND archisobasedir=@@INSTALL_DIR@@ archisolabel=@@ISO_LABEL@@ nomodeset vga=normal @@BOOT_CMDLINE@@
